name: ainsighter
description: Ainsighter mobil uygulamasÄ±

publish_to: "none" # Remove this line if you wish to publish to pub.dev

version: 1.0.0+1

environment:
  sdk: ">=2.11.0 <3.0.0"

dependencies:
  flutter:
    sdk: flutter
  flutter_localizations:
    sdk: flutter

  cupertino_icons: ^1.0.2
  provider: ^5.0.0
  dio: ^4.0.0
  shared_preferences: ^2.0.6
  intl: ^0.17.0
  image_picker: ^0.8.3+2
  connectivity: ^3.0.6
  http: ^0.13.3
  fluro: ^2.0.3
  flutter_svg: ^0.22.0
  cached_network_image: ^3.1.0
  simple_animations: ^2.0.0
  shimmer_animation: ^2.1.0+1
  google_fonts: ^2.1.0
  font_awesome_flutter: ^9.1.0
  mask_text_input_formatter: ^2.0.0
  lottie: ^1.1.0
  get_it: ^7.2.0
  dropdown_search: ^0.6.3
  bubble_tab_indicator: ^0.1.6
  curved_navigation_bar: ^1.0.1
  rflutter_alert: ^2.0.4
  flutter_rating_bar: ^4.0.0
  carousel_slider: ^4.0.0
  url_launcher: ^6.0.16
  sliding_sheet: ^0.5.2
  flutter_staggered_grid_view: ^0.4.1
  full_screen_image: ^1.0.2
  data_table_2: ^2.2.1
  fl_chart: ^0.55.1
  flutter_share: ^2.0.0
  infinite_scroll_pagination: ^3.2.0
  image_cropper: ^1.3.1
  pin_code_fields: ^7.4.0
  uni_links: ^0.5.1
  syncfusion_flutter_sliders: ^20.2.50
  currency_text_input_formatter: ^2.1.7
  flutter_masked_text: ^0.7.0
  webview_flutter: ^3.0.4
  selectify:
    path: ./packages/selectify

dev_dependencies:
  flutter_test:
    sdk: flutter

flutter:
  uses-material-design: true

  assets:
    - assets/image/
    - assets/icons/
    - assets/language/

  fonts:
    - family: Poppins
      fonts:
        - asset: assets/font/Poppins-Light.ttf
          weight: 300
        - asset: assets/font/Poppins-Regular.ttf
          weight: 400
        - asset: assets/font/Poppins-Medium.ttf
          weight: 500
        - asset: assets/font/Poppins-SemiBold.ttf
          weight: 600
        - asset: assets/font/Poppins-Bold.ttf
          weight: 700
